========================
Pooled Storage Resources
========================

List, Searching of Pooled storage resources are done through the ``/v1/pooled_storage``

List Pooled Storage Resources
=============================

.. rest_method::  GET /v1/pooled_storage/

Return a list of Pooled Storage Resources, this list generated by Valence controller from resource pool.
By default, this query will return resources with their id, name, and description.

Normal response codes: 200

Error response codes: badRequest(400), unauthorized(401), forbidden(403)

Request
-------

Response
--------

.. rest_parameters:: parameters.yaml

    - id: pooled_storage_drive_id
    - name: pooled_storage_drive_name
    - description: pooled_storage_drive_description
    - capacity: drive_capacity

