List Pooled Resource Details
=============================

.. rest_method::  GET /v1/pooled_storage/{resource_ident}

Shows details for a pooled storage drive.
This will return the full representation of the drive.

Normal response codes: 200

Error response codes: badRequest(400), unauthorized(401), forbidden(403)

Request
-------

.. rest_parameters:: parameters.yaml

    - resources_ident: pooled_storage_drive_id
    - fields: fields

Response
--------

.. rest_parameters:: parameters.yaml

    - id: drive_uuid
    - name: drive_name
    - description: drive_description
    - capacity: drive_capacity
    - health_status: drive_health_status
    - num_logcal_drives: logical_drive_number

